4 (7) (8) For purposes of this section:
5 (a) County correctional officer means a correctional officer
6 employed by a high-population county whose:
7 (i) Position obligates such employee to maintain order and custody
8 of inmates in a county jail; and
9 (ii) Duties involve regular and direct interaction with high-risk
