5 amended to read:
6 81-12,110 (1) Except as provided in subsection (3) of this section,
7 a private nonprofit corporation or an inland port authority created under
8 the Municipal Inland Port Authority Act may apply to the director to
9 become designated as an iHub. The director shall accept applications
